[We are very happy to receive this authoritative and detailed explanation
of the case. We still wonder whether airport malaria is really that rare
-- in Australia & elsewhere -- or whether it is usually not suspected and
therefore, in contrast to this case, the diagnostic blood smears are not
done? - Mod.JW]
